              cupiditate beatae.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
          <h2>Ingredients</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>2 boneless, skinless chicken breasts</li>
            <li>8 oz fettuccine pasta</li>
            <li>2 cups heavy cream</li>
            <li>1 cup grated Parmesan cheese</li>
            <li>2 cloves garlic, minced</li>
            <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
            <!-- Add more ingredients as needed -->
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
          <h2>Instructions</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Season the chicken breasts with salt and pepper.</li>
            <li>In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium-high heat.</li>
            <li>
              Add the chicken breasts and cook until golden brown and cooked
              through.
            </li>
            <li>Remove the chicken from the skillet and set aside.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </article>

